Nigerian singer, Damini Ebunoluwa Ogulu, popularly known as Burna Boy, has given a reason why he did not join the Nigerian army. Burna, while showing off his aiming skills on Thursday, shared how good a ‘shooter’ he would have been if he joined the army. Sharing a photo on his Instagram page, the African Giant said he did not join the army because he does not like to take orders. Burna boy wrote: “Just to let you know I could have been in the army as a good shooter but no, I don’t like taking orders.”